parameters.name: CurrentPage
parameters.description: The number of the page to return. Default value: 1.

parameters.name: ExportType
parameters.description:
The type of archived information. Valid values:

*   **suspiciousExport**: alert event

parameters.name: Lang
parameters.description:
The language of the content within the request and response. Valid values:

*   **zh**: Chinese
*   **en**: English

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries to return on each page. Default value: 1.
